<s-1 id="RM00000138001BX_01_0033" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00003AK00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL UPPER INSTRUMENT PANEL SUB-ASSEMBLY
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>for Automatic Air Conditioning System:</ptxt>
<ptxt>Connect the connector.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Attach the 5 guides and 6 claws to install the upper instrument panel.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the 4 screws &lt;A&gt;.</ptxt>
